4b9ce301e" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-iqseJM dvrCre pf-66_"><p class="sc-eZhRLC kPmrGB pf-67_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-hKumaY imecqU pf-69_">Yes, all our statutory and mandatory childcare courses, training and qualification are externally peer-reviewed and accredited by the CPD Certification Service (CPDUK). <br><br>Some sector-specific courses and programmes are also accredited by relevant organisations, including RoSPA, IATP, IFE, IIRSM, Gatehouse Awards and Training Qualifications UK (TQUK). Please check the course overview section for details about the accrediting or awarding body.&nbsp;<br><br>The <span style="font-weight: bold;"><a href="https://cpduk.co.uk/providers/the-mandatory-training-group" target="_blank">CPD Certification Service (CPDUK)</a></span> accredits all of our statutory and mandatory training courses as conforming to universally accepted Continuous Professional Development (CPD) guidelines.<br><span style="font-weight: bold; color: rgb(0, 41, 102);"><br></span></span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-egiyK kKHsVi pf-70_"><button type="button" class="sc-kDTinF iZLlzd pf-71_ pf-anchor" data-header-id="5f799e1a-a4b9-4e30-9ebf-9ea867bf5b74" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-plus pfa-arrow"></i><span>How to book for your statutory and mandatory childcare courses, training and qualification?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="5f799e1a-a4b9-4e30-9ebf-9ea867bf5b74" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-iqseJM dvrCre pf-73_"><p class="sc-eZhRLC kPmrGB pf-74_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-hKumaY imecqU pf-76_">To enrol our statutory and mandatory childcare courses, training and qualification through our website, please add the selected course(s) to the basket. From there, you will be redirected to the secure checkout page, where you can pay using a credit or debit card. <br><br>&nbsp;• Are you booking the course for another person?<br>
<br>If you are booking the course for another person, you must state their full name and email address in the notes section of the 'basket' area. Once we get the learner's details, our system will allocate the course(s) to the correct person.
<br><br>&nbsp;• Booking confirmation.<br>
<br>Once your payment has been confirmed, you will receive a booking confirmation email with a receipt immediately after your purchase. You will also receive an email with further instructions, including your unique login credentials to access your learner account ( you can start your course within 3 to 5 minutes of booking). You must then follow the instructions and log in to your learner account, where the course(s) booked will be ready for you or your staff to begin.
<br><br><span style="color: rgb(0, 41, 102); font-weight: bold;"><a href="https://www.mandatorytraining.co.uk/collections/course-bundle-offers-online-training-courses-programs" target="_blank">Click here for more Statutory and Mandatory Childcare Courses, Training and Qualification&nbsp;</a></span><br></span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-egiyK kKHsVi pf-77_"><button type="button" class="sc-kDTinF iZLlzd pf-78_ pf-anchor" data-header-id="301ebf9e-a867-4f5b-b466-2d16f4f6bfc5" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-plus pfa-arrow"></i><span>How long can I have access to your statutory and mandatory childcare courses, training and qualification?
</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="301ebf9e-a867-4f5b-b466-2d16f4f6bfc5" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-iqseJM dvrCre pf-80_"><p class="sc-eZhRLC kPmrGB pf-81_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-hKumaY imecqU pf-83_">When you are assigned to our statutory and mandatory childcare courses, training and qualification, you will have 365 days of unlimited access to the training materials and the end of course assessment for no extra charge. For individual statutory and mandatory childcare courses, training and qualifications orders, the course materials expire after 365 days from the day of purchase.<br><br>You can start your statutory and mandatory childcare courses, training and qualifications at any time suitable for you (within 365 days of purchasing the course).<br><br>From the day you purchase the course, you have access to the learning materials and assessments for 365 days.
<br><span style="font-weight: bold;"><br><span style="color: rgb(0, 41, 102);"><a href="https://www.mandatorytraining.co.uk/collections/course-bundle-offers-online-training-courses-programs" target="_blank">Click here for more Statutory and Mandatory Childcare Courses, Training and Qualification&nbsp;</a></span><br></span></span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-egiyK kKHsVi pf-84_"><button type="button" class="sc-kDTinF iZLlzd pf-85_ pf-anchor" data-header-id="5b74662d-16f4-46bf-852b-918338eeb2da" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-plus pfa-arrow"></i><span>Do you get a certificate after completing your statutory and mandatory childcare courses, training and qualification?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="5b74662d-16f4-46bf-852b-918338eeb2da" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-iqseJM dvrCre pf-87_"><p class="sc-eZhRLC kPmrGB pf-88_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-hKumaY imecqU pf-90_">On completion of each statutory and mandatory childcare courses, training and qualification, you have to take the end of course assessment and achieve a pass mark of 80% to be able to download a CPD certificate in PDF form, unless otherwise specified in the overview section of the course.</span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-egiyK kKHsVi pf-91_"><button type="button" class="sc-kDTinF iZLlzd pf-92_ pf-anchor" data-header-id="bfc52b91-8338-4eb2-9afd-7217b5a4bce2" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-plus pfa-arrow"></i><span>Are your statutory and mandatory childcare courses, training and qualifications purely done online?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="bfc52b91-8338-4eb2-9afd-7217b5a4bce2" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-iqseJM dvrCre pf-94_"><p class="sc-eZhRLC kPmrGB pf-95_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-hKumaY imecqU pf-97_">Yes, all our statutory and mandatory childcare courses, training and qualifications are delivered online. We do not provide any classroom or face-to-face training.
</span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-egiyK kKHsVi pf-98_"><button type="button" class="sc-kDTinF iZLlzd pf-99_ pf-anchor" data-header-id="b2dafd72-17b5-44bc-a224-8ae66bcc475e" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-plus pfa-arrow"></i><span>Can I do these statutory and mandatory childcare courses, training and qualification at my own pace?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="b2dafd72-17b5-44bc-a224-8ae66bcc475e" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-iqseJM dvrCre pf-101_"><p class="sc-eZhRLC kPmrGB pf-102_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-hKumaY imecqU pf-104_">Unlike many e-learning portals, our LearnPac LMS allows learners to complete their statutory and mandatory childcare courses, training and qualification at their own pace, in their own time, and on any device of their choice. Yes, you can complete your childcare courses, training and qualifications at your own pace, in your own time. You can leave the course and start where you left off. You do not have to restart the online course from the beginning.<br><span style="color: rgb(0, 41, 102);"><br></span><span style="font-weight: 700;"><a href="https://www.mandatorytraining.co.uk/collections/course-bundle-offers-online-training-courses-programs" target="_blank">Click here for more Statutory and Mandatory Childcare Courses, Training and Qualification&nbsp;</a></span><br></span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-egiyK kKHsVi pf-105_"><button type="button" class="sc-kDTinF iZLlzd pf-106_ pf-anchor" data-header-id="bce2248a-e66b-4c47-9ed8-8226e19dae16" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-plus pfa-arrow"></i><span>Are your statutory and mandatory childcare courses, training and qualification recognised as valid CPD?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="bce2248a-e66b-4c47-9ed8-8226e19dae16" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-iqseJM dvrCre pf-108_"><p class="sc-eZhRLC kPmrGB pf-109_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-hKumaY imecqU pf-111_">All our statutory and mandatory childcare courses, training and qualification are approved by the CPD Certification Service (CPDUK). All our children's services online training courses, programmes and qualifications are externally peer-reviewed and approved by the CPD Certification Service (CPDUK).<br><br>
These childcare courses, training and qualifications comply with the universally accepted <b><a href="https://cpduk.co.uk/providers/the-mandatory-training-group" target="_blank">Continuous Professional Development (CPD)</a></b> guidelines.
<br><br>Our CPD certificates are recognised internationally and can be used to provide evidence for compliance and audit.
</span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-egiyK kKHsVi pf-112_"><button type="button" class="sc-kDTinF iZLlzd pf-113_ pf-anchor" data-header-id="475ed882-26e1-4dae-9638-335265364e84" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-plus pfa-arrow"></i><span>How long are the certificates of your childcare courses, training and qualifications valid for?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="475ed882-26e1-4dae-9638-335265364e84" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-iqseJM dvrCre pf-115_"><p class="sc-eZhRLC kPmrGB pf-116_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-hKumaY imecqU pf-118_">Some industries/sectors specify how often you must undertake training and the validity of certificates. An example is the Safeguarding Adults Level 3 training, which has to be renewed every three years. <br><br>The certificate validity (where applicable) is specified in the course description (check course overview section). <br><br>For the majority of our online courses, the certificates do not have an expiration date. For example, some sectors, such as first aid, health and social care, require their employees to complete statutory and mandatory training annually, biannually or every three years. Where applicable, we will indicate the recommended renewal date on your certificate.
</span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-egiyK kKHsVi pf-119_"><button type="button" class="sc-kDTinF iZLlzd pf-120_ pf-anchor" data-header-id="ae163833-5265-464e-84f9-49b7c1a0ca01" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-plus pfa-arrow"></i><span>Are your cstatutory and mandatory childcare courses, training and qualification recognised outside the UK?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="ae163833-5265-464e-84f9-49b7c1a0ca01" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-iqseJM dvrCre pf-122_"><p class="sc-eZhRLC kPmrGB pf-123_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-hKumaY imecqU pf-125_">Yes, all our statutory and mandatory childcare courses, training and qualification are internationally recognised and verifiable for CPD hours completed. The content of our online childcare courses, training and qualifications have been independently peer-reviewed and certified as conforming to universally accepted Continuing Professional Development (CPD) guidelines.<br>
<br><b><a href="https://www.mandatorytraining.co.uk/" target="_blank">The Mandatory Training Group</a></b> is the leading UK provider of accredited statutory and mandatory training courses for all sectors, including health, safety and wellbeing, social care, education, local government, and many more.
<br><br><span style="font-weight: 700;"><a href="https://www.mandatorytraining.co.uk/collections/course-bundle-offers-online-training-courses-programs" target="_blank">Click here for more Statutory and Mandatory Childcare Courses, Training and Qualification&nbsp;</a></span><br></span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-egiyK kKHsVi pf-126_"><button type="button" class="sc-kDTinF iZLlzd pf-127_ pf-anchor" data-header-id="4e84f949-b7c1-40ca-8184-a039140b6cbd" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-plus pfa-arrow"></i><span>Can a non-resident of the UK take the statutory and mandatory childcare courses, training and qualification?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="4e84f949-b7c1-40ca-8184-a039140b6cbd" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-iqseJM dvrCre pf-129_"><p class="sc-eZhRLC kPmrGB pf-130_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-hKumaY imecqU pf-132_">Yes, a non-resident of the UK can take our statutory and mandatory childcare courses, training and qualification as long as they have internet access. There are no restrictions for non-UK residents. All our childcare courses, training and qualifications are internationally recognised and verifiable for CPD hours completed.</span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-egiyK kKHsVi pf-133_"><button type="button" class="sc-kDTinF iZLlzd pf-134_ pf-anchor" data-header-id="ca0184a0-3914-4b6c-bd80-72cf61a27c68" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-plus pfa-arrow"></i><span>Do you offer practical training for your statutory and mandatory childcare courses, training and qualification?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="ca0184a0-3914-4b6c-bd80-72cf61a27c68" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-iqseJM dvrCre pf-136_"><p class="sc-eZhRLC kPmrGB pf-137_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-hKumaY imecqU pf-139_">Our statutory and mandatory childcare courses, training and qualification are only suitable for individuals wishing to improve their theoretical knowledge and may be used in conjunction with a practical based session as blended learning. If your training policy and local authority guidance state you need a practical based session alongside the theoretical knowledge assessment (which is strongly recommended), then candidates will have to source that separately as we do not offer classroom-based training solutions.</span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-egiyK kKHsVi pf-140_"><button type="button" class="sc-kDTinF iZLlzd pf-141_ pf-anchor" data-header-id="6cbd8072-cf61-427c-a8b5-330e92030c00" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-plus pfa-arrow"></i><span>Will I be qualified to work in a children's home once I completed one of your statutory and mandatory childcare courses, training and qualification?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="6cbd8072-cf61-427c-a8b5-330e92030c00" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-iqseJM dvrCre pf-143_"><p class="sc-eZhRLC kPmrGB pf-144_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-hKumaY imecqU pf-146_">Our online statutory and mandatory childcare courses, training and qualification are ideal for refreshers and learners looking to up-skill their theoretical knowledge. Please note that our children's services e-Learning courses do not qualify you to be a health care support worker. It is also a mandatory refresher package for those who are already working in the field.
</span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-egiyK kKHsVi pf-147_"><button type="button" class="sc-kDTinF iZLlzd pf-148_ pf-anchor" data-header-id="7c68b533-0e92-430c-8094-120a1740a2ad" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-plus pfa-arrow"></i><span>Are your statutory and mandatory childcare courses, training and qualification suitable for unqualified individuals?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="7c68b533-0e92-430c-8094-120a1740a2ad" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-iqseJM dvrCre pf-150_"><p class="sc-eZhRLC kPmrGB pf-151_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-hKumaY imecqU pf-153_">The target audience for each statutory and mandatory childcare courses, training and qualifications will be stated in the overview of each course. <br><br>We offer a wide range of statutory and mandatory childcare courses, training and qualifications for unqualified individuals. The majority of our current statutory and mandatory childcare courses, training and qualifications are Continuing Professional Development (CPD) modules and programmes. These online courses range from:<br>
<br>&nbsp;• Awareness (Level 1 - Introductory),
<br>&nbsp;• Intermediate (Level 2), and
<br>&nbsp;• Advanced (Level 3-5).
<br><br>We strongly recommend that unqualified individuals start by completing the Level 1 modules before the intermediate and advanced modules.
</span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-egiyK kKHsVi pf-154_"><button type="button" class="sc-kDTinF iZLlzd pf-155_ pf-anchor" data-header-id="0c009412-0a17-40a2-ad22-b46088b21e30" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-plus pfa-arrow"></i><span>Are your statutory and mandatory childcare courses, training and qualification counted as recognised qualifications?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="0c009412-0a17-40a2-ad22-b46088b21e30" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-iqseJM dvrCre pf-157_"><p class="sc-eZhRLC kPmrGB pf-158_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-hKumaY imecqU pf-160_">All our statutory and mandatory childcare courses, training and qualification are approved by the CPD Certification Service (CPDUK). Please note that our courses are ideal for learners looking to up-skill their theoretical knowledge and is ideal for refreshers. Learners will have to attend a practical session and gain a full qualification for this.</span></p></div></div><div data-pf-type="Accordion.Content.Wrapper" class="sc-egiyK kKHsVi pf-161_"><button type="button" class="sc-kDTinF iZLlzd pf-162_ pf-anchor" data-header-id="a2ad22b4-6088-421e-b023-cad13b5bd69a" data-active="false" data-pf-type="Accordion.Header"><i class="pfa pfa-plus pfa-arrow"></i><span>Are there end of course assessments on your statutory and mandatory childcare courses, training and qualification?</span></button><div data-pf-expandable="true" data-id="a2ad22b4-6088-421e-b023-cad13b5bd69a" style="display:none" data-pf-type="Accordion.Content" class="sc-iqseJM dvrCre pf-164_"><p class="sc-eZhRLC kPmrGB pf-165_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-hKumaY imecqU pf-167_">Each online module or training programme around statutory and mandatory childcare courses, training and qualification has an assessment(s) and CPD certification. Pass marks and coursework will be specified in descriptions of individual courses. There is an 'End of Course Assessment' for each module/course.
<br><br>After completing the learning materials, you will be redirected to the 'End of Course Assessment' section.
<br><br>On successful completion of the 'End of Course Assessment' (achieving a pass mark of 80% or more), you will be able to download, save or print your CPDUK accredited certificate. Please note that you MUST go through the course materials first before attempting the End of Course Assessment.
</span></p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div data-section-id="pf-a6ce" data-pf-type="Section" class="sc-ihINtW bFPXVO pf-168_"><div style="--cw:1170px" class="sc-fvpsdx hSLMtg"><div class="sc-cTAqQK cFxQA-d pf-169_ pf-r pf-r-eh" style="--s-xs:15px" data-pf-type="Row"><div class="pf-c" style="--c-xs:12;--c-md:12;--c-lg:12"><div data-pf-type="Column" class="sc-kjOQFR ctEqvM pf-170_"><h3 data-pf-type="Heading" class="sc-nVkyK bhIDty pf-171_"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-hKumaY imecqU pf-173_">Contact Us</span></h3><p class="sc-eZhRLC kPmrGB pf-174_" data-pf-type="Paragraph"><span data-pf-type="Text" class="sc-hKumaY imecqU pf-176_">Still have some questions which you would like us to help you with?</span></p><div data-pf-type="Custom.HTML" class="sc-clIzBv iQyrr pf-177_"><!--[if lte IE 8]>
